      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a dependable daily driver for someone looking for value over aesthetics. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and some fading on the clear coat in certain areas. Inside, the cabin is functional but exhibits typical wear and tear, including some staining on the upholstery and minor scuffing on the dashboard. Mechanically, it remains sound and has been regularly serviced, though it lacks the refinement of a newer model. It is a solid, honest car that is ready for the road.",
