    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, truly a showroom-quality specimen that has been treated with the utmost care. The exterior paint is flawless, with no chips, scratches, or swirl marks, and the body panels are perfectly aligned. Inside, the leather is supple and free of any wear, with all electronics and features functioning exactly as they did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, it is perfect, having followed a rigorous maintenance schedule with full documentation included. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks and drives like it is brand new.",
