    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've got to see this beauty in person\u2014it is honestly in incredible shape and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I've babied this car since day one, and it's been kept in a climate-controlled garage, so the paint is still sparkling and the interior is absolutely flawless. It drives like an absolute dream! I'm looking for a new home for it where it'll be just as loved. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 43500.0,
