    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This is an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the naturally aspirated S54B32 inline-six with individual throttle bodies. This example has undergone a comprehensive preventative maintenance suite, including rod bearing replacement, a full VANOS overhaul, and a proactive rear subframe reinforcement. The Getrag six-speed manual transmission shifts with bolt-action precision, paired with a perfectly balanced limited-slip differential. The suspension geometry remains true, with all bushings providing the sharp, communicative feedback expected of a factory-fresh chassis. This vehicle represents a rare opportunity to own a mechanically synchronized icon in its most visceral form.",
      "price": 48500.0,
