    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional 2018 Porsche 718 Cayman in Graphite Blue Metallic. This vehicle is in showroom condition, having been meticulously kept in a climate-controlled garage and driven only on fair-weather weekends. The exterior paint retains its deep, glass-like luster thanks to a professional ceramic coating, with absolutely zero stone chips, scratches, or swirl marks. Inside, the black leather interior remains pristine; the sport seats show no signs of bolster wear, and the cabin still carries that distinct 'new car' aroma. Every surface, from the Alcantara headliner to the brushed aluminum trim, is flawless and free of any tactile wear. Mechanically, this Cayman is perfect, featuring a fully documented service history from authorized Porsche centers and very low mileage. It comes complete with both original keys, the factory window sticker, and a custom-fitted indoor car cover. This is a rare opportunity to own a modern classic that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the showroom floor.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
